ory><category>吕洞宾</category><category>纯阳真人</category><category>摘要</category><category>道</category><category>丹道</category></item><item><title>元道经 注解</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/reading/%E5%85%83%E9%81%93%E7%BB%8F%E6%B3%A8%E8%A7%A3/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/reading/%E5%85%83%E9%81%93%E7%BB%8F%E6%B3%A8%E8%A7%A3/</guid><description>太上老君元道真经注解 合明子隐芝内秀注 释题曰：元者，本也，始也。道者，太上真一之道也。经者，径也，本始之真元。此经最妙，故曰真经。 元道者，老君</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>元道经</category><category>炁體源流</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category><category>丹道</category></item><item><title>太乙金华宗旨-道藏续编</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E5%A4%AA%E4%B9%99%E9%87%91%E5%8D%8E%E5%AE%97%E6%97%A8/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E5%A4%AA%E4%B9%99%E9%87%91%E5%8D%8E%E5%AE%97%E6%97%A8/</guid><description>金华宗旨序 道在目前，身体自得，何劳身外寻求哉。人身为三才合一之身，造物赋我，其用甚大。我人日具而不知，圣人悯之，征诸一身以示之。盖谓道在一身</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>太乙金华宗旨</category><category>吕洞宾</category><category>纯阳真人</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category><category>丹道</category></item><item><title>道家静坐冥想修炼丹道开玄关一窍</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/reading/%E9%81%93%E5%AE%B6%E9%9D%99%E5%9D%90%E5%86%A5%E6%83%B3%E4%BF%AE%E7%82%BC%E4%B8%B9%E9%81%93%E5%BC%80%E7%8E%84%E5%85%B3%E4%B8%80%E7%AA%8D/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/reading/%E9%81%93%E5%AE%B6%E9%9D%99%E5%9D%90%E5%86%A5%E6%83%B3%E4%BF%AE%E7%82%BC%E4%B8%B9%E9%81%93%E5%BC%80%E7%8E%84%E5%85%B3%E4%B8%80%E7%AA%8D/</guid><description>道家功夫“贵在从虚空中收积先天一气于身中，然后以吾人之神与此气配合炼养之，为时既久，则神气合为一体，而大丹始成。” 但先天一气 “不在心肾，而在</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>玄关</category><category>丹道</category><category>道</category></item><item><title>金花的秘密</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%87%91%E8%8A%B1%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%98%E5%AF%86/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%87%91%E8%8A%B1%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%98%E5%AF%86/</guid><description>译者按：《太乙金华宗旨》共有十三章，卫礼贤只翻译了前八章，且有个别段落没有译出来，后面五章卫礼贤觉得价值没有那么大而未译出。《慧命经》全书共</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>金花的秘密</category><category>太乙金华宗旨</category><category>吕洞宾</category><category>纯阳真人</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category><category>丹道</category></item><item><title>青华秘文</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%9D%92%E5%8D%8E%E7%A7%98%E6%96%87/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%9D%92%E5%8D%8E%E7%A7%98%E6%96%87/</guid><description>玉清金笥青华秘文金宝内炼丹诀 紫阳真人张伯端撰 远师真人王邦叔授 东和希古渔人刘元一受 序 远师真人王邦叔，不知何许人也。时年十九，侍紫阳真人为弟子。</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>青华秘文</category><category>张伯端</category><category>紫阳真人</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category><category>南宗</category><category>丹道</category></item></channel></rss>